<div>   
<p>       <span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">如今，当有人提到人工智能</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">引起社会</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">变革潜力时，他们很可能是在谈论机器学习</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">中的人工神经网络</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。当</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">一</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">篇文章</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">谈人工神经网络</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">突破性进展时，作者</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">很</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">可能指的是深度学习。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">人工</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">神经网络是一种非线性统计建模工具，可以用于</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">发现</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">输入和输出之间的关系，或在大型数据库中</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">发现</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">模式。人工神经网络已应用于统计模型开发、自适应控制系统、数据挖掘模式识别和不确定性下的决策。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">深度学习是基于人工神经网络和表示学习的一系列机器学习方法的一部分。学习可以是有监督的、半监督的或无监督的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">甚至强化学习的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><strong><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">【深度学习</span></span></strong><strong><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">有别于传统机器学习</span></span></strong><strong><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">】</span></span></strong></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">有人称，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">实际上，深度学习是一种称为神经网络的人工智能方法的新名称，这种方法已经流行了</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">70</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">多年了”。但是，这样的说法并不准确。深度学习有别于传统机器学习。这里的“传统机器学习”，是指</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">世纪普通的神经网络，或浅层神经网络。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的确，计算机与大脑的关系，曾经吸引了</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">世纪</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">40</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年代计算机先驱的关注。例如，</span></span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;">1945年6月</span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">约翰</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">·冯·诺伊曼（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">John von Neumann</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）在《</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">EDVAC</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">报告草稿》首次描述现代计算的关键体系结构概念时，就使用了“</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">memory</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（记忆）”，“</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">organ</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（器官）”和“</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">neuron</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（神经元）”等生物学术语。冯·诺伊曼生前还撰写《计算机与人脑》未完成稿，从数学的角度解析了计算机与人脑神经系统的关系。又如，</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">1943</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年，沃伦·麦卡洛克（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">Warren McCullough</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）和沃尔特·皮茨（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">Walter Pitts</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）首次提出神经网络，他们</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的神经元模型，能够实现布尔逻辑语句。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">第一次重大的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">神经网络</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">突破，出现在</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">世纪</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">60</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年代中期，苏联数学家亚历克赛·伊瓦克年科（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">Alexey Ivakhnenko</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）在他的助手拉帕（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">V.G.Lapa</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）的帮助下创建了小型但功能</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">较</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">强的神经网络，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">采用</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">有监督深度前馈多层感知器的学习算法。</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">而单层感知机是</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">世纪</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">50</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年代</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">罗森布拉特</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">发明的。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">上世纪</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">80</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年代初，约翰·霍普菲尔德（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">John Hopfield</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">循环</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">神经网络（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">recurrent neural networks</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）引起了轰动</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，紧接着特里</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">·塞伊诺夫斯基（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">Terry Sejnowski</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）的程序</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">NetTalk</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">可以发音英语单词。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">2006</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年，卡内基梅隆大学教授、计算机科学家杰弗里·辛顿</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">使用</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">了</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“深度学习”这个词，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">此后，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“深度学习”术语很快广泛流行</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">虽然，这个术语并非辛顿第一个使用的，早在</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">1986</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年，</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">R.</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">德克特（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">R. Dechter</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）的一篇论文就将“深度学习”一词引入机器学习。</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">2000</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年，艾森伯格（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">Aizenberg</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）等人首次将其引入人工神经网络。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">21</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">世纪的深度学习与传统神经网络区别在哪里呢？</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">首先，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">人工神经网络包含输入层和输出层之间的隐藏层。传统的神经网络</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">只</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">包含</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">一</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个或</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">几</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个隐藏层。深度学习是一个非常大的神经网络，包含多</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">得多的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">隐藏层（通常为</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">150</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个），它们可以存储和处理更多信息。</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">这是深度学习有别于传统神经网络的最重要的一点。</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">因此，名称</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">深层</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">”用于此类网络。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">其次，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">深度学习不需要手</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">工</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">提取特征，而直接将图像作为输入。</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">这是深度学习有别于传统神经网络的另一点。</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">图</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">1</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">描述了在机器学习和深度学习中识别对象所遵循的过程。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">第三，深度学习</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">需要高性能的</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">GPU</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">和大量数据。特征提取和分类是通过称为卷积神经网络（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">CNN</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）的深度学习算法进行的。</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">CNN</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">负责特征提取以及基于多个图像的分类。当数据量增加时，深度学习算法的性能也会提高。相反，当数据量增加时，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">传统</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">学习算法的性能会降低。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><img width="567" height="344" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"> </span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">图</span></span><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">1 </span></span><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">机器学习与深度学习</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="background: #FFFFFF; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">在机器学习中，需要</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">提供给</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">算法更多的信息（例如，通过执行特征提取）来做出准确的预测。在深度学习中，由于采用了</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">深度</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">人工神经网络的结构，算法可以通过自身的数据处理学习如何做出准确的预测。表</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">1</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">更详细地比较了这两种技术：</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="background: #FFFFFF; color: #0000FF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">表</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">1 </span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">深度学习与传统机器学习比对</span></span></p><table><tbody><tr class="firstRow"><td valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold;">传统</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 等线; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">保持了</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">他对建造的热爱，包括建造飞机、电子乐器和机器人的兴趣爱好。从</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">2013</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">12</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">月起，他被</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">Facebook</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">聘用</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">从事人工智能研究，现在是</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Facebook</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的首席</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">AI</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">科学家。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">200</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">0</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年，约书亚</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">·本吉奥撰写了一篇里程碑式的论文《神经概率语言模型》（</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">参考资料</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">[2]</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">），对自然语言处理任务（包括语言翻译、问答和视觉问答）产生了巨大而持久的影响。自</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">2010</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年以来，本吉奥关于生成性深度学习的论文，特别是与他的博士</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">生</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">伊恩</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">·古德费洛（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">Ian Goodfellow</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）共同开发的生成性对抗网络（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">GAN</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">），在计算机视觉和计算机图形学领域引发了一场革命。本吉奥本人曾与他人共同创立了几家初创公司，其中最著名的是</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">2016</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年的</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">Element AI</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，该公司为深度学习技术开发工业应用程序。</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">2017</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年约书亚·本吉奥和伊恩·古德费洛、亚伦·库维尔出版了《深度学习》一书，是深度学习领域奠基性教材，又名“花书”，被誉为深度学习的“圣经”。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><strong><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">【</span></span></strong><strong><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">21</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">世纪</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">10</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年代</span></span></strong><strong><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">深度学习</span></span></strong><strong><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">技术突破</span></span></strong><strong><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">】</span></span></strong></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">以物体识别为标志，从传统机器学习到深度学习的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">转变，大约发生在</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">21</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">世纪</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">10</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年代初。</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">但</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">在</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">2010</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年之前几年，已经已经为此转变做了准备，包括算法（“深度学习”）、建立图像数据库（“</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">ImageNet</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">”）和提升算力（“</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">GPU</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">”）。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">大约在</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">2016</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年之后</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">深度学习</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">显示出令人印象深刻的结果，首先是在语音识别，然后是计算机视觉，最近是在自然语言处理方面。由此产生的算法，在学术和工业应用领域，引发了一场</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">深度学习</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">革命。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">以下简单回顾发展历程。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">2006</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年，杰弗里·辛顿等人说。发表了一篇论文（</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">参考资料</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">[1]</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，展示了如何训练一个能够以最先进的精度识别手写数字的深度神经网络（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">>98%</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）。他们称这种技术称为“深度学习”。深度神经网络是大脑皮层一个非常简化的模型，由一叠人工神经元层组成。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">2008</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年，吴恩达（</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Andrew NG</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）在斯坦福的研究小组开始提倡使用</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">GPU</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">来训练深层神经网络，以将训练时间缩短数倍。这为在海量数据上进行有效的训练带来了深度学习领域的实用性。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">2009</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年，斯坦福大学的人工智能教授李</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">飞飞</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">Fei Fei Li</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）推出了</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">ImageNet</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">李飞飞</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">是一位华裔美国计算机科学家。</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">ImageNet</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">项目是一个大型可视化数据库，设计用于视觉对象识别软件的研究。超过</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">1400</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">万张图片已经被该项目手工标注，包含</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">20000</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">多个类别。李</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">飞飞</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">教授说：</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“我们的愿景是，大数据将改变机器学习的工作方式。数据驱动学习。”</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><img width="473" height="216" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"> </span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">图</span><span style="font-family: 等线;">3 李飞飞</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">2011</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年，约舒亚</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">·本吉奥等</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">在他们的论文</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“深度稀疏整流神经网络”中表明，</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">ReLU</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">激活函数可以避免消失梯度问题。这意味着，除了</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">GPU</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">深度学习社区</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">还有另一个工具，来避免</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">深度</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">神经网络训练时间过长和不切实际的问题。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">2012</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">和他的学生</span></span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">亚历克斯</span><span style="font-family: 等线;">·克里热夫斯基（</span></span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;">Alex Krizhevsky）</span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">以及另外一个学生，</span></span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">建立了一个名为</span>AlexNet的计算机视觉神经网络模型，参加ImageNet的图像识别比赛。参赛者将使用他们的系统处理数以百万计的测试图像，并以尽可能高的精度识别它们。AlexNet以不到亚军一半的错误率赢得了比赛。</span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">这场胜利在全球引发了一场新的深度学习热潮。</span></span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;">AlexNet是在多年前由雅恩·</span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">勒村</span></span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">建造的</span>LeNet5</span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">（</span></span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">图</span><span style="font-family: 等线;">4A）</span></span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">基础上，发展和改进的</span></span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">。</span></span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;">AlexNet</span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">是一种用于图像分类的多层卷积神经网络</span></span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">（</span></span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">图</span><span style="font-family: 等线;">4B）</span></span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">。</span></span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;">AlexNet架构包括5个卷积层和3个完全连接层</span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">（对比而言，</span></span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;">LeNet是一个5层的卷积神经网络模型，它有两个卷积层和3个全连接层</span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">）</span></span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><img width="567" height="228" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"> </span></p><p style="text-align: center; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><strong><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">(A)</span></span></strong></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><img width="567" height="207" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"> </span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><strong><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">(B</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">)</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">图</span><span style="font-family: 等线;">4 </span></span><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">Le</span></span><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">N</span></span><span style="color: #0000FF; text-align: left; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">      2012</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年，</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">Google Brain</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">发布了一个被称为“猫实验”的不寻常项目的结果。</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">该</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">项目探索了</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“无监督学习”的困难。猫实验使用了分布在一个由</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">16000</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">台电脑组成的网络，通过观看</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">YouTube</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">视频中的</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">1000</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">万张“未标记”的图片，训练自己识别猫。在训练结束时，发现最高层的一个神经元对猫的图像有强烈的反应。该项目的创始人</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">吴恩达</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">说：</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“我们还发现了一种对人脸反应非常强烈的神经元。”。</span></span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">2014</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">生成型对抗性神经网络也称为</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">GAN</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，是由伊恩·古德费洛（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">Ian Goodfellow</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）创建的。</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">GANs</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">凭借其合成真实数据的能力，在时尚、艺术、科学等领域开启了一扇全新的深度学习应用之门。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">2016</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Deep</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">M</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">ind</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的深度强化学习模型</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">AlphaGo</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">在复杂的围棋游戏中击败了人类冠军。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">2019</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年，</span></span><span style="font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 等线;">本吉奥、勒村和辛顿</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">因其在深度学习和人工智能领域的巨大贡献</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">,</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">获得</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">2018</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年度</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">图灵奖。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">2020</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年，</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">OpenAI</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">发布</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">GPT-3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，这是一种具有</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">1,750</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">亿个参数的自然语言深度学习模型。同年，</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">DeepMind</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">公司开发的人工智能程序</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">AlphaFold2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">预测蛋白质结构堪比实验室水平。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><strong><span style="color: #0070C0; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 21px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">【</span></span></strong><strong><span style="color: #0070C0; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 21px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">结语</span></span></strong><strong><span style="color: #0070C0; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 21px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">】</span></span></strong></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">世纪探索感知机和人工神经网络的科学家，都是基于这样的想法，即类似的网络可能像人的大脑一样，能够学习识别物体或执行其他任务。深度学习在</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">21</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">世纪</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">10</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年代取得了辉煌</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的成就，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">成为</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">驱动</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">人工智能繁荣</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的动力。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">深度学习的</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">成功已经用于</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">在照片中</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">识别</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">物体或分类，自动驾驶汽车，游戏，自动机器翻译，图像字幕生成，文本生成，不同化学结构的毒性检测，预测蛋白质的 3D 结构形状等。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">深度学习</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">已经</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">变成了一种颠覆性的技术。总有一天，无人驾驶汽车会比你更了解道路，驾驶技能更高；深入的学习网络会诊断你的疾病</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“漫谈”的四篇博客</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（人工智能的第一项工作、感知机的兴衰、神经网络的复苏和深度学习的辉煌）</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，回顾了神经网络和深度学习的从</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">世纪</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">40</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年代至今的发展的若干重要事件，可以看出：（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）多学科协同研究很重要。（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）对新技术不要仓促否定，也不要夸张宣传。（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">科学家的坚持不懈的努力，造就了今天深度学习的辉煌和人工智能的繁荣。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">深度学习的繁荣，也反映在出版有许多有关深度学习的图书，特别是有关深度学习编程的工具箱，对进一步学习提供很多便利（例如，</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">[3]</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">[4]</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">和</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">[5]</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><strong><span style="color: #0070C0; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">参考资料：</span></span></strong></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255);
